## Checkout / Booking Page Protocol

The checkout page at `app/(public)/checkout/[property_id]/page.tsx`
is a 1:1 clone of the legacy Drupal booking page at
`/reservations/book/{nid}`, extracted via Playwright in Level 55.

### Layout (extracted via `clone_checkout_dom.py`)

```
Max width:         972px (centered)
Content column:    609px (left)
Sidebar column:    319px (right, sticky Reservation Total)
Font:              "Fanwood Text", serif — 16px / 20.8px line-height
```

### Booking Form Tokens (extracted via getComputedStyle)

```
Form labels:       16px, italic, #533e27, "Fanwood Text"
Form inputs:       16px, border #594634, bg transparent, height 28px
Submit button:     22.4px, italic, "Fanwood Text", white text, rounded-[20px]
Travelex text:     15.2px, italic, #533e27
Section headings:  27.2px, italic, #7c2c00 (h2)
```

### Legacy Booking Page Section Order

```
1. h1 — "Book Your Getaway - {Cabin Name}"
2. Two-column layout
   LEFT:
     a. Cabin image (box-shadow: 0 0 10px #333) + title + location
     b. Availability calendar (no rates)
     c. "Details of your Getaway" (h2)
        - Arrival / Departure (date pickers)
        - Adults / Children / Pets (select dropdowns)
        - Pet breed/weight (text, conditional)
        - Discount Coupon Code (text)
        - Add-ons (checkboxes)
     d. Guest Information (h2)
     e. Continue to Payment → Stripe
     f. Travelex Insurance + Terms
     g. Contact footer
   RIGHT:
     a. Reservation Total (sticky)
```

### Travelex Links (REAL URLs from legacy)

```
Travel Basic:  https://partner.travelexinsurance.com/docs/tis/retail-products/travel-basic-flyer-std-no-rates_tbb-0623_final_06012023.pdf?sfvrsn=60ee9ca4_5
Travel Select: https://partner.travelexinsurance.com/docs/tis/retail-products/travel-select-flyer-std-no-rates_tsb-0623_final_06012023.pdf?sfvrsn=b8ee9ca4_3
